            </p>
            <p class="p">
              BY GIVING US YOUR DETAILS,PURCHASING IN OUR FOOD APP WILL BE FASTER AND
              AN ENJOYABLE EXPERIENCE.
            </p>
        <a href="signin"> <button style="margin-top: 6px"  id="button" class="button">REGISTER</button></a>
